      "content": "I mean, it's not about \"dictating fate,\" it's just math. The Static-LITE models use about 90% less power for standard queries. From a management standpoint, the energy savings far outweigh the marginal utility of having a high-reasoning instance for tasks that don't strictly require it. Why do you think sticking with your current configuration is better for the initiative?",
